PHAM VI GIAY PHEP / SCOPE OF THIS LICENSE
=========================================

Repo nay chua HAI thu khac nhau ve phap ly. Doc ky truoc khi clone ve dung.

1. MA NGUON - cap phep theo MIT (toan van ben duoi)
---------------------------------------------------
   admin.html, scripts/, supabase/, _redirects, _headers, docker/,
   package.json, va phan CO CHE cua TuyenSinh-eDA2026.dc.html
   (dinh tuyen tab, lop phu CMS, logic doi soat, phan quyen RLS).

   Dung, sua, ban, deploy thoai mai. Khong can xin phep.

2. NOI DUNG KHOA HOC VA HINH ANH - KHONG cap phep
--------------------------------------------------
   Nhung thu duoi day thuoc ve AI VIETNAM va nhung nguoi trong anh.
   MIT o muc 1 KHONG ap dung cho chung. Ban KHONG duoc phep dung lai:

   - ava/*.jpg, ava/*.jpeg
     Chan dung 4 giang vien co that. Quyen hinh anh thuoc ve ho, khong phai
     thu chu repo cap phep duoc. Dung anh nguoi khac de quang cao khoa hoc
     cua ban la vi pham quyen hinh anh, bat ke giay phep phan mem ghi gi.

   - Ten nguoi that trong TuyenSinh-eDA2026.dc.html (phan Giang vien)

   - assets/logo-full.png, assets/logo-mark.png
     Nhan hieu. Nhan hieu khong bao gio di theo giay phep ma nguon.

   - assets/dongson-*.svg, assets/dongson-*.png, assets/dongson-set.jpg,
     assets/Overview_eDA2026.jpg, assets/video/*.jpg

   - docs/eDA-2026-Syllabus.md, docs/eDA-2026-Syllabus.html
     Giao trinh.

   - Toan bo chu tren trang tuyen sinh: mo ta khoa, hoc phi, cam ket,
     danh gia hoc vien.

   TRUOC KHI DEPLOY BAN CLONE, PHAI THAY HET MUC 2 BANG NOI DUNG CUA BAN.
   Xem muc "Doi thanh khoa cua ban" trong README.md.

3. support.js, image-slot.js - sinh boi cong cu khac
-----------------------------------------------------
   Hai file nay do toolchain "dc-runtime" / "omelette starter" sinh ra,
   khong phai viet cho repo nay ("GENERATED ... do not edit"). Giay phep
   theo cong cu sinh ra chung. Neu ban phat hanh lai ban clone ra ngoai,
   tu kiem tra dieu khoan cua toolchain do truoc.


